This package is available on the CRAN repository for installation from the following link:
https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=CytobankAPIstats

The R package can easily be installed from the R Console command line or using RStudio with the following command:
install.packages("CytobankAPIstats",dep=T)

Package functions can be accessed used library(CytobankAPIstats) once the package is installed.
